    <title>This is for my gril</title>
    <url>/2021/10/06/This%20is%20for%20my%20gril/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>2岁1个月21天</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% meting &quot;004AFf1D1AU7I4&quot; &quot;tencent&quot; &quot;playlist&quot; &quot;mutex:false&quot; &quot;listmaxheight:340px&quot; &quot;preload:auto&quot; &quot;theme:#ad7a86&quot;%&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tosspi/img@main//img/8871635580063_.pic_hd.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:10%;" />

<p>服了我闺女的感性的一天</p>
<p>今晚睡前她妈妈和她在翻手机里她小时候的照片  </p>
<p>一边看一边在给她讲小时候的故事</p>
<p>她俩都看的特别认真</p>
<p>因为时间原因 妈妈说先看这些吧 剩下的明天再看</p>
<p>于是她妈妈就总结了一下说：</p>
<p>你小时候爸爸妈妈很爱你 </p>
<p>大了爸爸妈妈更爱你 </p>
<p>希望你健康长大 不要生病 </p>
<p>等妈妈总结完成看我闺女 </p>
<p>我闺女满眼泪水 </p>
<p>我问她：你怎么了？  </p>
<p>我闺女就哇哇大哭了</p>
<p>我…………最后哭睡了 …………</p>
<p>最后我想说：时间可真快啊  我的女孩已经这么大了</p>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/TossPi/blogimg/raw/master/img/8761635579792_.pic.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:25%;" /><img src="https://gitee.com/TossPi/blogimg/raw/master/img/8711635579786_.pic.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:25%;" /><img src="https://gitee.com/TossPi/blogimg/raw/master/img/8751635579792_.pic.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:25%;" /></p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tosspi/img@main//img/8881635580066_.pic_hd.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:10%;" /><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tosspi/img@main//img/8871635580063_.pic_hd.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:10%;" /><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tosspi/img@main//img/8861635580050_.pic_hd.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:10%;" /></p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tosspi/img@main//img/8851635580047_.pic_hd.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:10%;" /><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tosspi/img@main//img/8841635580046_.pic_hd.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:10%;" /><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tosspi/img@main//img/8831635580044_.pic_hd.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:10%;" /></p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tosspi/img@main//img/8821635580042_.pic_hd.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:10%;" /><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tosspi/img@main//img/8811635580041_.pic.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:10%;" /><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tosspi/img@main//img/8781635580038_.pic_hd.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:10%;" /></p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tosspi/img@main//img/8771635579793_.pic_hd.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:10%;" /><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tosspi/img@main//img/8741635579791_.pic_hd.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:10%;" /><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tosspi/img@main//img/8731635579789_.pic_hd.jpg" alt="alt Markdown" style="zoom:10%;" /></p>
